michelin and fesvial , sets to the port of the helmet
the tyre manufacturer michelin , in collaboration with the spanish foundation for road safety , fesvial , has launched a campaign to encourage the wearing of the helmet , mainly among motorcyclists more young people , as said today the two bodies .
this initiative aims to promote awareness of the importance of the wearing of the helmet , since it is the only part of protection to avoid head injuries , or even death , in case of an accident in two wheels .
michelin said that the campaign was in keeping with his commitment to road safety , which goes beyond the design and manufacture of products increasingly safe " , and said that it is contributing to this goal by other actions to educational and informative .
this new campaign to encourage the port of the helmet on two wheels , under the motto " to be but not to be , " a first stage in which include posters will be distributed in more than 500 garages effect , in order to guarantee the widest spread .
finally , michelin has pointed out that the road safety is a constant concern " for the company , because as a tyre manufacturer for vehicles on two wheels , one of its main objectives is to develop products increasingly safe .
the sale of light commercial vehicles to go
after nearly two years ago , the light commercial vehicle market is beginning to see a little bit of light at the end of the tunnel .
the 9 425 vehicles registered in november in spain is an increase of 12.6 % compared to 2008 and , what is more important , they represent the first increase after 22 consecutive month of decline , according to the figures of the patronal manufacturers association anfac and ganvam , the dealers .
however , we need to alter the good news , because the reference for the comparison , the month of november 2008 , has been particularly bad , with a reduction of 60 % compared to the previous year .
as a result , despite the events of the last month , the immatriculations accumulated during the 11 months are 40 % in less than those of the previous year .
since january , if you add all vehicles coming into the category of light commercial vehicles - derived from cars , light pick-up , vans , fourgons and light trucks to windows 95 853 have been sold .
high clouds that affect their request did not eliminated . in fact , although they are bought by individuals , most of the purchases are made by small and medium sized enterprises , which pay in nearly 100 % of the cases thanks to an external financing .
and , in addition to the restrictions involved by restricting credit , we need to add other factors such as the rise in the unemployment rate and the continuation of the bad economic situation .
faced with this situation , and in contrast to the cars , the aid to the purchase of the 2000e were used .
as well as individuals , independent and those who wish to acquire a commercial vehicle slightly less than 3.5 tonnes with a level of carbon dioxide emissions , which does not exceed 160 grams per kilometre , can also benefit from it , but the number of operations speaks for itself .
yesterday , in ganvam , it recalled once again the need for the government to pay special attention to these vehicles and also the industrial vehicles , trucks and buses .
the dealers ' association provides a year 2010 similar to that ends , for which she found a fall in sales - passenger vehicles and the suv of 19 % .
the emergency brake is now required aid
as has occurred with the system anti-lock restrictions abs and it will take place with the esp , stability control systems of aid in the emergency brake compulsory will form part of the european cars .
mandatory they are already on the newly registered passenger cars and light commercial vehicles , while for the rest of the vehicles , a period has been set up to the end of february 2011 .
the measure , imposed by the european union , is intended to strengthen the protection of pedestrians , even if , because of its course of action , it can also help to avoid many blows back .
the assistant to the emergency brake is increasing pressure on the brakes in urgent cases detected in the system through the shot in the foot of the driver .
but they do not always keeps the pressure until the end of time .
according to a study conducted by the manufacturer of parts for cars bosch , one third of the drivers involved in an accident did not rely on the brakes before the collision , and half of them did not benefit from its full force .
up to 1 , 100 accidents
intervention of aid , in revancha , requires the maximum of the braking system , cutting the distance which needed to stop the car .
according to a study by the eu , if all the cars are equipped with this type of points , up to 1 100 fatal accidents in which pedestrians are involved could be prevented each year .
this reduction would be even more important with the ' popularisation of smart emergency braking systems : it is a sinister about four with the injured would be avoided .
in this case , the vehicle is equipped with a system that , thanks to a radar or a camera , detect obstacles and to prevent the driver , in addition to slightly on the brakes .
if the driver is applied , it help in increasing the pressure on the , if it is necessary .
if it does not act , and that the crash is inevitable , it has a maximum effort on the brakes in order to minimize the damage .
