new tools for the expertise of the car
in these days of bad weather , and accidents , the cars garages are not the only winner .
every day , thousands of cars , which have suffered a grim are brought up in a garage , where an expert to assess the damage and the cost of repairs .
every event is different , and the calculation of the cost of parts and the time of workforce may be a long and complex process .
calculating compensation to shoulder the cost of between 20,000 and 30,000 euros , including the parts and the workforce may take two or three hours .
on the other hand , with the assistance of the most recent computer tools , it would be a matter of minutes .
it is for this reason that almost 100 % of the experts to use this kind of systems .
service providers and solutions for the evaluation of claims and maintenance are dedicated to collecting information provided by the manufacturers , and then deal with them and offer them to customers in the form of a useful tool .
in spain , audatex , leader of the north american solera group , is the company ; 80 % of the estimates are carried out with its products .
other companies to compete in the field of evaluation and tools for the development of information on the sector are gtmotive and eurotax .
the work with the information provided by the manufacturers is far from simple .
according to audatex eduardo velázquez , director of trade , the company in spain , with 63 manufacturers and importers , and every one of them provides them with information in a different format .
in addition , the amount of data to deal with continues to grow , so that in the past five years , more than versions , variations and motorisations have been launched in the past 15 years .
when a new car fate in the market , the companies are at work .
it is a very difficult work , because you need to catalogue every thousand pieces of the vehicle and put his prize .
in addition , it sets a graphic image " smart " of each model on which we can click on the different parts of a car to tourism .
if he is a model sold in huge numbers , the work could be ready in a week if they are moving very quickly .
if it is a little car sold , it can take three or four months . at the moment , audatex has information about 99,2 % of the cars sold in spain .
one of the most exclusive models , for example , they have information about the porsche , but not of the ferrari and lamborghini .
on the vehicles on the road , a figure exceeds the 99 % .
to do the work of documentation and preparing the databases , audatex has eight centers spread all over the world in spain , france , germany , the united states , brazil , mexico , china and japan , and all of them are specialized in some brands .
the national headquarters is located , to alcobendas - madrid - .
there , more than 100 technicians or general , experts in mechanical work simultaneously in three computer screens .
audatex invests 90 million every year to develop such databases .
every month , 2.5 million of data is stored , and the customers are actualisations every two days .
drafting of this huge flow of information to allow them to give them various uses , and to offer a variety of products .
the most frequent application for the repair and maintenance , but in different countries , there is also the tools for the management of the components of residual or damage to calculate the value vénale or a car .
the only company that has a guide to making inquiries about the value of cars of opportunity eurotax in spain .
audatex does not offer in our countries , but it does so in the united states .
in view of the products offered by audatex , it is easy to get an idea of the type of support it can provide to the workers in the sector .
this company provides 10 different tools , the flagship is audaplus evaluation standard , the solution of the fires , intended for the experts .
there are cars , bikes , industrial light and heavy vehicles .
in addition to the cost of repair parts , it takes into account the time valued by the manufacturer or the scales of paint .
this tool comes in line with its use , for every estimate .
the cost of 5.75 euros , the highest for customers who use it little , a maximum 10 times per month .
then every insurance company , which operates the thousands of expertise , is negotiating a price with audatex .
other products , such as audavin , allow the full identification of a vehicle and equipment , with whom he is out of the assembly line , only because of its number of windows .
audaglass focuses on the glass of cars , and audasubastas is an open in the industry about internet server , which allows enchérir on vehicles declared wrecks .
his office of statistics is very useful to identify the tendencies , conducting tests géo-démographiques or knowledge of the current problems by mark or model .
it is possible to study , for example , how many models of a determined went in the garage to mark a failure or how many have suffered serious disasters for a certain period .
motivates gt is the only spanish company which is devoted to the development of this type of tools .
it is selling , among other things , gt estimate , which is also intended to experts and provides digital images , as well as access to documents , prices and official time of the manufacturer .
gt motivates is a company of the einsa group , founded in 1971 , as a provider of services and solutions evaluation of the claims , and devoiture outages or maintenance .
the guide gt evaluation is a product of historic reference on the market .
the company is working with 24 , 000 users in garages , 3 100 specialists and 53 insurance companies .
its volume of business has increased at a rate of 20 percent per year over the past three years , and it has made a turnover of 10,8 million euros in 2008 .
at the beginning of the last year , it has made the process of globalization , with the establishment of an office in paris .
on his side , audatex was born in germany in 1966 , and is located in spain in 1979 .
according to the sources of the company , 62 percent of its turnover is carried out in europe and the rest of the world , and the remaining 38 % of north and south america . it works with 900 insurance companies and 33 , 000 , of which 3,000 are garages in spain .
the turnover of the world solera - audatex , sidexa , informex abz , hollander and ims s " amount to $ 557 million , more than 3.3 % in 2008 .
in our country , the company is set to receive 19.1 million euros , or 7.2 percent to more than last year .
in 2005 , the group solera was quoted on the stock market of 1 billion dollars , today , its actions are estimated at a total of 2 , 400 million dollars .
for 2007 , it is a hand on the new york stock exchange and is part of the standard & poor 's index of reference .
auctions on the internet of cars accidentées
